metadata.name: Exogalactic Warlords #01
metadata.description:
Part of the series: Exogalactic Warlords

The Violet Crane Princess, warlord of Atupal, planet of the Triple Star System.

STROB is a professional CG artist since more than 25 years, credited in movies, TV shows and games such as Journey to the Center of the Earth, Mars Rising, Prince of Persia, Myst IV, Rainbow Six. He also worked on commercials for brand such as Cadillac, Subway, Danone, Kellogg’s, Nestlé, 
Campbell's, Aero and Oh Henry. He also contributed to YouTube hit such as Iron Baby, Little Antman and I Pet goat II.

PNG, 896x2304 pixels.
